title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 49] Post-Punk
description:
As promised, for lovers of Post-Punk. In case you're questioning, yes this is the same Dead or Alive, before You Spin Me Round days when they started as a Post-Punk band. Quite different than their synthpop materials. Enjoy your weekend with the 80's music!



Danse Society - Seduction [1982]

Dead or Alive - Doors of Perception (1980-1982)

Shoc Corridor - Anthology

The Royal Family & The Poor - North-West Soul [1980]
